reviewText: Super Fast Shipping - Item Just as Described - Recommended Seller 5 stars*****

This show is of a low quality and the discs are poor quality DVD-Rs (burned discs) in cheap thin packs with color copied inserts. I purchased this show and it didn't work on my DVD player because it was burned - I had to return it to Amazon. [...]. People who are thinking about buying this series should know that it is not as good as others out there. Save your money.

I found these dvd's on amazon and I'm glad I did. This is a great show and the editing rivals any network tv show. They didn't find too much evidence in these episodes but enough to leave me satified. And the way these were edited make me want to watch them over and over. Good Job and I do leave wanting more.
